---
title: Vietnamese-Style Caramelised Beef Bowl with Garlic Rice, Rainbow Slaw & Mint
description: This flavour-packed beef bowl will transport you to the streets of Vietnam. Seasoned beef and a refreshing slaw, topped with aioli and all of it is sitting on top of a helping of fragrant garlic rice. There’s a new combination in every bite!

